          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0637P0_20020704_GCR_52' title='Link to this speech by Ms Elizabeth Barker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-elizabeth-barker" title="Ms Elizabeth Barker">Baroness Barker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
