          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-rodney-elton" title="Mr Rodney Elton">The Deputy Chairman (Lord Elton)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Thursday next at 4 p.m.</p><p>
            The Committee adjourned at twenty-nine minutes before eight o'clock.
          </p>
